title: Hallmark White Tissue Paper, 100 Sheets for Christmas Gift Wrap, Holiday Crafts and More
description: This classic white tissue paper adds the perfect accent to your gift any time of year and is great gift-wrapping staple to have on hand. It's perfect for wrapping delicate gifts, adding cushioning to presents, and for decorative fill in gift bags and baskets. Purchase includes 100 sheets of white tissue paper Each sheet of tissue paper measures 20 inches long by 20 inches wide. Created with high-quality paper materials, all Hallmark gifting products are made with paper from well-managed forests. For more than 100 years, Hallmark has been helping its customers make everyday moments more beautiful and celebrations more joyful.
